{"id": "1234723546190581800", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "848454386598412318", "author_name": "ruko9999", "author_bot": false, "content": "爆率不用 可以補爆傷", "timestamp": "2024-04-30T04:30:33.466000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1234723845538189354", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "848454386598412318", "author_name": "ruko9999", "author_bot": false, "content": "傻鯊的話 \n爆傷因為是個人 紅悸充爆傷就好\n專精沒那麼重要 某些角色就能特化一點  像是銀鑰衝頂的墨菲", "timestamp": "2024-04-30T04:31:44.836000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1234768861996519444", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 19, "author_id": "454232816893427713", "author_name": "sierrara", "author_bot": false, "content": "圖魯國家隊不用暴率嗎？我之前看到某個攻略 以為深海也要堆暴率:0", "timestamp": "2024-04-30T07:30:37.596000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["848454386598412318"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1234723546190581800", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1234769654153740298", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 19, "author_id": "848454386598412318", "author_name": "ruko9999", "author_bot": false, "content": "隱密.摯友.3啟螺湮 能產50~56%爆率了\n再配一個暴擊造物就很足了\n大不了等彌利補第4位\n界精200就很佔密契詞條了 其實能補的不多", "timestamp": "2024-04-30T07:33:46.461000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["454232816893427713"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1234768861996519444", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1234770214202249239", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "454232816893427713", "author_name": "sierrara", "author_bot": false, "content": "哦哦原來", "timestamp": "2024-04-30T07:35:59.987000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1234770993948524645", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "848454386598412318", "author_name": "ruko9999", "author_bot": false, "content": "不過這裡有個邏輯\n其實深海是可以4個人密契都帶全暴擊詞條\n差別跟界精就是 界精打穩跟前期\n在觸手長不夠多的時候 狂氣的打擊次數就很重要 但長滿後效益就會低\n而暴擊因為密契跟命輪是1/2效果\n全部帶滿還是挺可觀的 但相對\n當你沒暴擊就沒效果", "timestamp": "2024-04-30T07:39:05.893000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1234771122369728592", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "848454386598412318", "author_name": "ruko9999", "author_bot": false, "content": "至於那個好只能說看個人", "timestamp": "2024-04-30T07:39:36.511000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1234771394408222760", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "848454386598412318", "author_name": "ruko9999", "author_bot": false, "content": "傻鯊那套的邏輯又不一樣 \n跟其他界域的邏輯比較像\n輔助帶自己適合的效果\n主C帶爆傷紅悸頂傷害", "timestamp": "2024-04-30T07:40:41.370000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1234771602663804989", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "848454386598412318", "author_name": "ruko9999", "author_bot": false, "content": "所以密契是深坑 推薦深海界狂密契是可以給其他界域輔助用", "timestamp": "2024-04-30T07:41:31.022000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
